**  @SL  ( SELECT )
DELETE
CHANGE
ADD
**  @MS  ( ERR MSG )
ER01 PROCESS IS NOT INPUT
ER02 PROCESS IS NOT INPUT
ER03 PROCESS CODE DOES NOT EXISTIN PROCESS DATA
ER04 PROCESS CODE DOES NOT EXISTIN PROCESS DATA
ER05 INPUT PROCESS CODE / FACTORY CODE
ER06 PROCESS POST IS NOT INPUT
ER07 INPUT CORRECT FACTORY CODE
ER08 INPUT HEAT TREATMENT CONDITION (LOQ)
ER09 INPUT OQ CONDITIONS
ER10 INPUT HEAT TREATMENT CONDITION (OQ/LOQ)
ER11 INPUT LAN/AOQ CONDITIONS
ER12 INPUT LAN/AOQ CONDITIONS
ER13 INPUT SECOND SURFACE TREATMENT
ER14 INPUT KRO/JC/COS/SD/NP/TC PROCESS.
ER15 CHECK HEAT TREATMENT PROCESS
ER16 CHECK S.T.CODE AND PROCESS AND MACHINE #
ER17 INPUT SURFACE TREATMENT PROCESS
ER18 SECOND SURFACE TREATMENT CODE ERROR.
ER19 NOT EXIST IN QUENCHING CONDITION M/F. F7:IGNORE
